### ============================
### Slot Game Server API
### ============================

### 取得所有遊戲列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games
Accept: application/json

### 取得 Fortune Gods 遊戲資訊
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/fortune-gods
Accept: application/json

### 取得 Gates of Olympus 1000 遊戲資訊
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/gates-of-olympus-1000
Accept: application/json

### 取得 Super Ace 遊戲資訊
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/super-ace
Accept: application/json

### 取得 Legendary Creature 遊戲資訊
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/legend-creature
Accept: application/json

### 取得不存在的遊戲（應回 404）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/non-existent-game
Accept: application/json

### ============================
### Spin — Fortune Gods (6x5 Ways + Cascade)
### ============================

### Fortune Gods — 投注 20
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "fortune-gods",
  "betAmount": 20.0
}

### Fortune Gods — 投注 100
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "fortune-gods",
  "betAmount": 100.0
}

