### ============================
### Balance
### ============================

### 查詢玩家餘額
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/balance
Accept: application/json

### ============================
### Error Cases
### ============================

### 不存在的遊戲（應回 404）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "non-existent-game",
  "betAmount": 20.0
}

### 投注金額為 0（應回 400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "fortune-gods",
  "betAmount": 0
}

### 投注金額為負數（應回 400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "fortune-gods",
  "betAmount": -10.0
}

### 餘額不足（投注超大金額，應回 400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "fortune-gods",
  "betAmount": 999999.0
}

### 缺少 gameId（應回 400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "betAmount": 20.0
}
